title: Person of Interest - What are you doing in my house ? (05x12)
author: POI - Best Of
comment:
"You're going to take down the internet!!"
"Been there, done that." 
BEST QUOTE EVER!
I love the "Evil Finch" theme in these last few episodes of Season 5. Real tense.
You should always fear a man who can totally control you without raising his voice.

1:26 "Wait, who are you?"
A) "Batman."
B) "A figment of your imagination."
C) "I'm just like you, a man who sold the world."
Oh man, the way Harold asks about Grace to The Machine is just heartbreaking. I am so glad The Machine conspired to reunite them in life.
